<title><![CDATA[ New Myanmar govt proposes keeping some junta curbs on protests]]></title>
<link><![CDATA[ http://zeenews.india.com/news/world/new-myanmar-govt-proposes-keeping-some-junta-curbs-on-protests_1884665.html ]]></link>
<description><![CDATA[  Myanmar democracy champion Aung San Suu Kyi is facing criticism from rights groups and student activists who say her ruling party is planning to retain restrictions on free speech once wielded against it by the country`s former junta.
 ]]></description>
